# --- Model weights -------------------------------------------------------
# The research checkpoints are ~267 MB each, over GitHub's 100 MB hard limit.
# They ship as GitHub Release assets instead; see models/README.md.
models/*.keras
models/*.h5
models/*.pkl

# The demo model (26 MB) IS committed -- it is what makes `demo/app.py` runnable
# straight after clone. Do not add demo/*.keras here.

# Generated SavedModel export (rebuild with demo/export_saved_model.py)
demo/saved_model/

